What you need to know:

Granada have slumped to ninth in La Liga but have enjoyed a brilliant debut European campaign, notably beating PSV Eindhoven away in the group stage and eliminating Napoli in the last 32 before defeating United boss Ole Gunnar Solskjaer's old club Molde of Norway in the round of 16.Unai Emery won the Europa League in three consecutive years with Sevilla and took Arsenal to the 2019 final.